---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Case Studies — Mike Hnath">

  <div class="section">
    <div class="page-header">
      <div class="page-title">Case Studies</div>
      <div class="page-count">7 projects</div>
    </div>
    <div class="page-subtitle">Selected case studies across brand strategy, performance media, GTM, and creative direction.</div>
    <div class="filter-bar">
      <button class="filter-pill active" onclick="filterWork(this,'all')">All</button>
      <button class="filter-pill" onclick="filterWork(this,'brand')">Brand</button>
      <button class="filter-pill" onclick="filterWork(this,'performance')">Performance</button>
      <button class="filter-pill" onclick="filterWork(this,'gtm')">GTM</button>
      <button class="filter-pill" onclick="filterWork(this,'design')">Design</button>
      <button class="filter-pill" onclick="filterWork(this,'web')">Web</button>
    </div>
    <div class="section-label" style="margin-bottom:10px">By the numbers</div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,minmax(0,1fr));gap:10px;margin-bottom:24px">
      <div class="stat-box" style="aspect-ratio:5/4"><div class="stat-num">$1.7M+</div><div class="stat-label">Paid media managed</div></div>
      <div class="stat-box" style="aspect-ratio:5/4"><div class="stat-num">15+ yrs</div><div class="stat-label">Brand &amp; marketing</div></div>
      <div class="stat-box" style="aspect-ratio:5/4"><div class="stat-num">$500K+</div><div class="stat-label">Client funding raised</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-row-label">Featured</div>
    <div class="work-grid" style="margin-bottom:24px">
      <a class="work-card" data-tags="brand,gtm" href="/Personal/case-studies/scandalous/">
        <div class="work-thumb">[Scandalous brand visual]</div>
        <div class="work-body"><div class="work-client">THIS · 9-year client</div><div class="work-title">Built a regulated CPG brand from concept through multi-state commercialization — investor materials, packaging, and go-to-market assets</div><div class="work-outcome">$500K+ raised · 11–13 SKUs · 5 states · anchor retainer</div><div class="work-meta"><span class="work-industry">Cannabis · Regulated consumer</span><span class="work-arrow">→</span></div></div>
      </a>
      <a class="work-card" data-tags="performance" href="/Personal/case-studies/pocn/">
        <div class="work-thumb" style="padding:0"><img src="/Personal/Images/POCN/pocn-cs-gfx-2.jpg" alt="" /></div>
        <div class="work-body"><div class="work-client">POCN · 2022–2024</div><div class="work-title">Migrated pharma media operations to a proprietary platform while managing $1.7M+ in campaign spend across 30 concurrent campaigns — driving significant annual cost savings</div><div class="work-outcome">$1.7M+ managed · 30 concurrent campaigns · 50+ pharma therapies</div><div class="work-meta"><span class="work-industry">Healthcare · Pharma</span><span class="work-arrow">→</span></div></div>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="section-row-label">All projects</div>
    <div class="work-grid">
      <a class="work-card" data-tags="gtm,brand" href="/Personal/case-studies/sigil/">
        <div class="work-thumb">[SIGIL Kickstarter]</div>
        <div class="work-body"><div class="work-client">Pine Island Games · 2023</div><div class="work-title">Took an original IP from concept to funded product — brand identity, game assets, and full campaign execution. Crowdfunded 3x the goal.</div><div class="work-outcome">$22K+ crowdfunded · full positioning + packaging + campaign</div><div class="work-meta"><span class="work-industry">Consumer · Gaming</span><span class="work-arrow">→</span></div></div>
      </a>
      <a class="work-card" data-tags="design" href="/Personal/case-studies/kraft-heinz/">
        <div class="work-thumb">[KH MiO digital shelf]</div>
        <div class="work-body"><div class="work-client">Kraft Heinz via Imaginary · 2020–2021</div><div class="work-title">Aligned digital shelf strategy with performance-driven creative — contributing to ~8% Amazon sales lift for MiO</div><div class="work-outcome">~8% Amazon lift · 800+ assets · 30 brands · 15 A+ pages</div><div class="work-meta"><span class="work-industry">CPG · eCommerce</span><span class="work-arrow">→</span></div></div>
      </a>
      <a class="work-card" data-tags="performance,gtm" href="/Personal/case-studies/triax/">
        <div class="work-thumb" style="padding:0"><img src="/Personal/Images/Triax/triax-cs-gfx-2.jpg" alt="Triax enterprise content" /></div>
        <div class="work-body"><div class="work-client">Triax Technologies · 2021–2022</div><div class="work-title">Rebuilt technical messaging and implemented marketing automation to help move Fortune 50 energy prospects into late-stage sales conversations.</div><div class="work-outcome">300% webinar growth · Hess &amp; Shell advanced · Salesforce + Pardot from zero</div><div class="work-meta"><span class="work-industry">B2B SaaS · Demand Gen</span><span class="work-arrow">→</span></div></div>
      </a>
      <a class="work-card" data-tags="brand,design" href="/Personal/case-studies/infinity/">
        <div class="work-thumb">[Infinity licensed brands]</div>
        <div class="work-body"><div class="work-client">Infinity Lifestyle Brands · 2018–2019</div><div class="work-title">Rebuilt product positioning and sales materials to transform a limited licensing portfolio into a scalable partnership engine</div><div class="work-outcome">$10M+ licensing ecosystem · 50+ SKUs · Disney, MLBPA, Viacom</div><div class="work-meta"><span class="work-industry">CPG · Licensed consumer</span><span class="work-arrow">→</span></div></div>
      </a>
      <a class="work-card" data-tags="brand,gtm" href="/Personal/case-studies/ark/">
        <div class="work-thumb">[Ark of the Covenant]</div>
        <div class="work-body"><div class="work-client">Ark of the Covenant · 2008–2016</div><div class="work-title">Built an independent brand from zero to a nationally touring act through full ownership of product, brand, operations, and growth</div><div class="work-outcome">350+ shows · 20K+ followers · 2 distribution deals · Mesa/Boogie endorsement</div><div class="work-meta"><span class="work-industry">Music · Independent</span><span class="work-arrow">→</span></div></div>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-top:24px;text-align:center"><a class="btn" href="/Personal/tools/" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" style="width:16px;height:16px;stroke:currentColor;fill:none;stroke-width:1.5;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;flex-shrink:0"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg>See the tools I use to make these happen<span style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.18);font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:9px;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:4px;font-weight:500;line-height:1.4">6</span></a></div>
  </div>

</Base>
